18.10.22  Río de Janeiro, das Laranjeiras
ARG - PAR 2:0 (0:0)
(8,000) Enrique Vignal BRA
ARG: Tesoriere - A.Celli, Sarasíbar - Chabrolín, Médici, Solari - Rivet, De Césari,Gaslini, E.Celli, Francia
PAR: Denis - Mena Porta, Paredes - Centurión Miranda, Fleitas Solich, Benítez Casco -Schaerer, Capdevila, López, Rivas, Erico
1:0 Francia 63, 2:0 Francia 79 p
NOTE: PAR left the field in the 79th minute in protest against the penalty sanctioned by the referee. Only Denis stayed in the field, but failed to save the shot.
NOTE: As URU withdrew, playoff needed between BRA and PAR to decide the champion.


Round: Final

